<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#82eb1969f2934f81852db70:DataActivityPurpose">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#DataActivityPurpose"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">82eb1969f2934f81852db70</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">We may share information if we think we have to in order to comply with the law or to protect ourselves. For example, we will share information to respond to a court order or subpoena. We may also share it if a government agency or investigatory body requests. Or, we might also share information when we are investigating potential fraud. This might include fraud we think has happened during a sweepstakes or promotion.</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

