  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">These sites and apps are not intended for children Our sites and apps are meant for adults We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13 If you are a parent or legal guardian and think your child under 13 has given us information you can email us here You can also write to us at the address listed at the end of this policy Please mark your inquiries COPPA Information Request</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

